    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A FPS multiplayer game where you can play with 40+ items/weapons that you can throw or eat (Some items are not recomended to eat). First you get some time to find items and prepare for the battle, when madness start and sky will be full of knifes, stones, woods, tables, completly everything. Try to survive, and kill as many players as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105380/extras/209e33128c91afbd07f48bb7624619ad.avif?t=1732910713\" width=720 height=720 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get reward from wins and go costumize your character with hats, backs and if you get sufficient amount of XP you can costumize your weapons. Also you can open loot boxes or doing quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105380/extras/9d817677003843dcd01d510e2eb7fd78.avif?t=1732910713\" width=718 height=408 /></span></p>",
